{"title": "Making Your Own Sour Cream Is Extremely Worthwhile", "author": "Claire Lower", "para": "I do not DIY without a reason. If I\u2019m going to make my own version of a commercially available product, it either needs to taste better than its store-bought counterpart, cost me fewer dollars, or align with my particular brand of laziness. This is why I don\u2019t make my own ketchup\u2014it\u2019s time consuming, not much cheaper and the end result is  , which is a perfect sauce. I thought I might have similar feelings about making my own sour cream, but I\u2019m not so ignorant anymore."}
